Current versions are available from http://psi.affinix.com/download.php
Version 0.12 was downloaded from
http://downloads.sourceforge.net/psi/psi-0.12.tar.gz

The orig.tar.gz is generated from the upstream tarball by removing
the following (windows-only) binary files, which where included without
source code:

	src/tools/idle/win32/idleui.dll
	src/tools/zip/minizip/win32/libz.a
	win32/tod.exe

